description:
This week on ANN, 33 individuals participate in the “Peddaling for Your Health” initative by cycling across Puerto Rico. Their goal: to raise funds for injured former triathlete and promote healthy living. 

Women worldwide participate in enditnow Emphasis Day on August 27, 2022, including women in northern Nigeria who peacefully marched against violence. 

Maranatha Volunteers International continues to impact communities worldwide through the building of churches, schools, and water wells. This year alone, Maranatha has provided clean water for over 200 communities. These stories and more coming up.

For more updates on worldwide Adventist news, subscribe to our Youtube channel. 

ANN is the official news channel of the Seventh-day Adventist Church. For all things Adventist news, visit https://adventist.news/
